body:
damn ...all three have demons in their past.
They need to muster up their courage and talk it out..Easy to say tho.

Just a rough guess from some dialogue i can read, so one of them has been suffering from the high expectation from their parent while the black haired little sister has always been jealous because her sister looks like she can do anything and got to be praised by everyone.

Pretty deep ngl
I want to know what's happening here, lol it's hentai without hentai logic, instead join them, the blonde got angry and slap the black haired bitch
This series is in serious need of a TL. I'm taking wild guesses here but damn, looks like both sisters(?) are hurt and guy needs to man up & stop being wishy-washy.
